org.dgfoundation.amp.reports

Class ReportCacher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.reports.ReportCacher

  • public class ReportCacher
extends java.lang.Object
    Report output cacher that uses a Guava-powered LRU softmap. The key of the report is a String token which is used as a old-style HashMap key with special treatment of null keys: null-keyed values are not saved to the cache. Naturally, null-keyed gets get a "miss" back.
